metadata.name: Unfinished Monkey Business 2023 #1/49
metadata.description: This artwork is a seamless blend of personal photography taken in London, street art created by the artist, and elements of artificial intelligence utilizing midjourney. A combination of various filters and other tools were skillfully employed to bring this piece to life. The artwork itself is a pasteup, which has been placed in both legal and non-legal locations on the streets of the UK. Despite its underground origins, this piece is a testament to the artist's exceptional technical abilities and their innate creativity. Furthermore, this artwork is a rare and exclusive physical print, limited to only 50 copies in existence, and was made available for purchase through the artist's website.
